title: Shall we invest 10 eth in fractions of NFT photo to become member of RAW dao?
body:
RAW is a new dao focused on high end photography. Some very famous photographers in the nft world have gathered here in collaboration with fingerprints dao (largest collection of autoglyphs among others).

Normally we only buy complete nft's. However, I would like to propose purchasing a fraction of Justin Aversano's twin picture to become member of the RAW dao. Why? 

I expect:
- Early access at new minting from top photographers. This has a great economic value.
- insider knowledge about new sales and releases 
- influence on development of nft photography by being able to vote and make proposals with our rights 
- strategic positioning of Jenny 

The fractions can always be sold again. Will probably only become more valuable.

With 10 eth we get 1% of the voting rights. 
In summary, with a relatively small investment, we will gain a lot of knowledge and we will be able to acquire very valuable photography art in the coming months.

More information: https://mirror.xyz/0x87a41F37f4195F8313751180151e56FA5ea5CF0c/aolQD_u5mrYpLwy1-gf-KsMP43fag8a5fgyldwDR8PU
